Scheme Now! v1.1.2 (March 14, 2008)
===================================

The documentation and installation instructions are available on the
Snow web site:

   http://snow.iro.umontreal.ca

Installation usually consists of these steps:

   % ./configure --site-root=$HOME/.snow-site --install-hosts=yes
   % make install
   % export PATH="$HOME/.snow-site/current/bin:$PATH"
